author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Bygghemma Group's IPO Set At SEK 47.50 Per Share
text:
March 27 (Reuters) - BYGGHEMMA GROUP NORDIC AB:
* OFFERING PRICE IN BYGGHEMMA GROUP’S INITIAL PUBLIC OFFERING SET AT SEK 47.50 PER SHARE - TRADING ON NASDAQ STOCKHOLM COMMENCES TODAY
* OFFERING PRICE CORRESPONDS TO A MARKET CAPITALISATION OF BYGGHEMMA GROUP OF APPROXIMATELY SEK 5,100 MILLION​
* ‍OFFERING COMPRISED 29,647,660 SHARES​ * ‍ASSUMING THAT OVER-ALLOTMENT OPTION IS EXERCISED IN FULL, VALUE OF OFFERING WILL AMOUNT TO ABOUT SEK 1,620 MILLION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
